      "content": "honestly im just so tired of pretending. like every single day is just this massive, exhausting performance to try and act like a normal person. it feels like i'm playing a game where everyone else has the rulebook and i'm just making it up as i go. i dont think i'll ever actually fit in. it's just... draining.",
